{"tid":1153599,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"【新蒲崗酒吧】7,500呎手工啤酒私竇！同陳冠希超似樣型男本地自釀啤酒廠＋酒吧","createTime":"2019-05-13T17:32:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T03:57:38.000Z","uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8bf557094c8e0c25ac9a53c506de05c6ccb7a701","tid":1153599,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T17:32:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://etw-image.nextdigital.com.hk/images/e-paper/20190508/large/1557306628_000b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fetw-image.nextdigital.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190508%2Flarge%2F1557306628_000b.jpg&h=027cd557&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n飲啤酒不再是麻甩佬的專利，其實懂得品嘗的話，手工啤酒也可以很講究。與一般大眾商業啤酒有別，手工啤酒相對少量生產，以人手釀製，講求品質與手藝，「Deadman Brewery」是本地自釀啤酒品牌之一，釀酒人Gerry本身加拿大留學時愛好喝啤酒，繼而親自落手自釀，製成品意外深得身邊朋友青睞，甚至打本給他釀酒，取名為「Deadman」，自嘲香港人工作營營役役，累得沒半條人命，猶如死人。<br />\n<br />\n酒吧的啤酒主要有3種，Pale Ale，偏美式風格，重花香味道，聞起來有少許熱帶果實的味道；Porte，加入了咖啡豆和奶香金萱茶釀造，味道跟鴛鴦很類近，聞起來重奶味，喝起來帶煙燻味和泥煤味；Wheat Beer，香蕉味加上很重的小麥味道，很適合香港的天氣，因為味道偏甜的關係，無論男女都會喜歡。"},{"pid":"601bb253528cc0bb27bde14a22aecbe7713bfb46","tid":1153599,"uid":242427,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T17:37:10.000Z","msg":"邊忽似希哥？冇L嘢呀？"},{"pid":"ba79f612d5fcd13307da8d186b2cd768ca811835","tid":1153599,"uid":29080,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T18:06:13.000Z","msg":"超似樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c40e8650dfb84a999b753491a6225f1073ac3232","tid":1153599,"uid":84673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T18:07:30.000Z","msg":"似樣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"229dda99e578ca7dfb990c4e8c7f87407272c5e7","tid":1153599,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T00:05:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"075188108bf2